###############################################
# FILTROS AVANÇADOS
###############################################

### 1. Busca básica (origem + destino)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&destination=Parintins
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Filtro por preço mínimo
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&minPrice=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Filtro por preço máximo
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&maxPrice=100
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Filtro por faixa de preço
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&minPrice=50&maxPrice=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Filtro por período - Manhã (6h - 12h)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&departureTime=morning
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Filtro por período - Tarde (12h - 18h)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&departureTime=afternoon
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Filtro por período - Noite (18h - 6h)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&departureTime=night
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Filtro por avaliação mínima do capitão
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&minRating=4.5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Filtro combinado - Preço + Período
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&minPrice=50&maxPrice=200&departureTime=morning
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Filtro combinado - Todos os filtros
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?origin=Manaus&destination=Parintins&date=2026-02-15&minPrice=50&maxPrice=200&departureTime=morning&minRating=4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Viagens econômicas (até R$ 50)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?maxPrice=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Viagens premium (capitão 4.5+ e preço alto)
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?minRating=4.5&minPrice=150
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Viagens matinais baratas
GET http://localhost:3000/trips?departureTime=morning&maxPrice=50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
